$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
$ Pinned-pinned column under axial load -- SOL 105 (Linear Buckling)
$
$ Geometry: L = 20 in, 0.5 in x 0.5 in square cross section.
$ Material: Al 6061-T6 (E=9.9e6 psi).
$ Loads: 100 lbf axial compression at the free end.
$ Constraints: Pinned-pinned (T1/T2/T3 at root; T2/T3 at tip).
$
$ Analytical Euler critical load (pinned-pinned):
$   P_cr = pi^2 * E * I / L^2
$   I = b*h^3 / 12 = 0.5 * 0.5^3 / 12 = 0.005208 in^4
$   P_cr = (pi^2) * 9.9e6 * 0.005208 / 400
$        = 1271 lbf
$ Eigenvalue lambda_1 from MYSTRAN should be ~12.71  (since the applied
$ load is 100 lbf and lambda * P_applied = P_cr).
$ ----------------------------------------------------------------------
SOL 105
CEND
TITLE = Pinned-pinned column - SOL 105 (Euler buckling)
SUBCASE 1
  STATSUB(BUCKLING) = 1
  SPC = 1
  LOAD = 10
  METHOD = 200
  DISPLACEMENT(PRINT,PLOT) = ALL
BEGIN BULK
$
PARAM,WTMASS,2.588-3
$
$ -------- Material --------
MAT1           1  9.9+6          .33    .098
$
$ -------- Property (0.5 in square) --------
PBARL,1,1,,BAR
,0.5,0.5
$
$ -------- Nodes (21 nodes along X, 1 in spacing) --------
GRID           1              0.      0.      0.
GRID           2              1.      0.      0.
GRID           3              2.      0.      0.
GRID           4              3.      0.      0.
GRID           5              4.      0.      0.
GRID           6              5.      0.      0.
GRID           7              6.      0.      0.
GRID           8              7.      0.      0.
GRID           9              8.      0.      0.
GRID          10              9.      0.      0.
GRID          11             10.      0.      0.
GRID          12             11.      0.      0.
GRID          13             12.      0.      0.
GRID          14             13.      0.      0.
GRID          15             14.      0.      0.
GRID          16             15.      0.      0.
GRID          17             16.      0.      0.
GRID          18             17.      0.      0.
GRID          19             18.      0.      0.
GRID          20             19.      0.      0.
GRID          21             20.      0.      0.
$
$ -------- Elements --------
CBAR           1       1       1       2      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           2       1       2       3      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           3       1       3       4      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           4       1       4       5      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           5       1       5       6      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           6       1       6       7      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           7       1       7       8      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           8       1       8       9      0.      1.      0.
CBAR           9       1       9      10      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          10       1      10      11      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          11       1      11      12      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          12       1      12      13      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          13       1      13      14      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          14       1      14      15      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          15       1      15      16      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          16       1      16      17      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          17       1      17      18      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          18       1      18      19      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          19       1      19      20      0.      1.      0.
CBAR          20       1      20      21      0.      1.      0.
$
$ -------- Constraints: pinned-pinned --------
$ Root pinned in T1/T2/T3, free in rotation
SPC1           1     123       1
$ Tip pinned in T2/T3, free in T1 (so the column can shorten)
SPC1           1      23      21
$
$ -------- Static load: 100 lbf compression at tip --------
FORCE         10      21       0   -100.      1.      0.      0.
$
$ -------- Eigenvalue extraction for buckling --------
EIGRL        200      0.    100.       3
$
ENDDATA
